Golden circle of Threat hunting:




Why is this hunt triggered?? Structures/ Unstructured/ Situational hunt?

What will we be hunting for? IOCs/ IOAs 

How? What tools and log sources will we be looking at for our hunt?

Threat hunting methodologies

Indicator based:

Indicators of Attack (IOAs): Structured

Indicators of Compromise (IOCs): Unstructured

Hypothesis driven:
Analytics based: AI/ ML/ UEBA

Intelligence based

Situational / Triggered induced
